==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underrate
<hw>Un`der*rate"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To rate too
low; to rate below the value; to undervalue.</def>
<rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underrate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Underrate
<hw>Un"der*rate`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A price less than
the value; <as>as, to sell a thing at an <ex>underrate</ex></as>.</def>
<rj><au>Cowley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underreckon</ent>⟦br⟧
